stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Invalid

    Invalid --> Shared : Read (fetch from RAM)
    Invalid --> Exclusive : Read (no other cache)

    Shared --> Modified : Write
    Shared --> Invalid : Other core writes

    Exclusive --> Modified : Write
    Exclusive --> Shared : Other core reads
    Exclusive --> Invalid : Other core writes

    Modified --> Shared : Other core reads (writeback)
    Modified --> Invalid : Other core writes (writeback)
